  m_Name: Day 3 Morning Wakeup
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  announcementId: dolos_day3_morning_wakeup
  text: Rise and shine, Technician Andromeda. Current time is 0700 hours. Please
    prepare for yet another productive day in service of the DOLOS Corporation, a
    subsidiary of the Erebus Holdings. Body temperature has decreased by 0.4% since
    the previous biometric scan. All systems are functional. Please proceed to your
    Aegis Collar Supplement Dispenser for your mandatory daily wellness protocol
    at your earliest convenience.
